# ReplyDebt

You are building ReplyDebt, a local-first personal inbox debt tracker.

## Core principles

- Build small, working increments.
- Do not rewrite unrelated files.
- Inspect existing files before editing.
- Prefer simple, boring architecture.
- No auth unless explicitly requested.
- No payments unless explicitly requested.
- No message sending.
- No message generation.
- No scraping private APIs.
- The app only detects likely pending replies from screenshots.
- Local-first and privacy-first.
- After every change, explain exactly how to test it manually.
